# SoulTrader Project Rules

## Virtual Environment
When executing Python commands in the sandbox, always activate the virtual environment at:
`~/Development/scratch/python/tutorial-env/`

Use: `source ~/Development/scratch/python/tutorial-env/bin/activate` before running Python commands.

## Code Creation
Even in agent mode, don't create code if the user only asks a question. Only create or modify code when explicitly requested to do so.

